item.title: James Gunn Reacts to Social Media Star Trisha Paytas Naming Her Son Aquaman: “That’s Cool”
item.description: Of the influencer’s eclectic baby name noice, the DC Studios boss said that he “hope[s] he does OK in school” because he “had a hard time with the last name Gunn.”
